fileimporter-specialpage: Title for the File Import special page.
fileimporter-cantparseurl: Error message shown on the special page when the URL entered can not be parsed.
fileimporter-cantimporturl: Error message shown on the special page when the URL entered can not be imported from.
fileimporter-exampleprefix: Prefix for the example URL contained within the URL text box on the special page.
fileimporter-submit: Text for the submit button on the special page.
fileimporter-import: Text for the import button on the special page.
fileimporter-importfilefromprefix: Prefix for the URL being imported from on the special page.
